## Public Interface

### Validation Script Entry Point

```python
# scripts/validate_production.py
def validate_production_deployment(
    docker_compose_path: str = "docker-compose.prod.yml",
    dockerfile_path: str = "Dockerfile.production",
    baseline_path: str = ".performance_baseline.json",
    config_dir: str = "config"
) -> ValidationReport:
    """
    Run comprehensive production deployment validation.

    Returns:
        ValidationReport: Contains pass/fail status for all checks with detailed diagnostics
    """
```

### Validation Report Structure

```python
@dataclass
class ValidationReport:
    timestamp: datetime
    overall_status: ValidationStatus  # PASS, FAIL, WARNING
    checks: List[ValidationCheck]     # Individual check results
    summary: str                      # Human-readable summary
    recommendations: List[str]        # Action items if any failures

@dataclass
class ValidationCheck:
    name: str
    status: ValidationStatus
    message: str
    details: Optional[dict] = None
    severity: ValidationSeverity      # CRITICAL, HIGH, MEDIUM, LOW
```

