## What This Does NOT Do

- ❌ **Does NOT modify** any production configuration files
- ❌ **Does NOT deploy** the application to any environment
- ❌ **Does NOT run** the full application (only validates configuration and runs unit/integration tests)
- ❌ **Does NOT test** hardware-dependent features (Astra, MIDI, DMX) - those are validated in earlier phases
- ❌ **Does NOT perform** load testing or stress testing (separate performance task)
- ❌ **Does NOT validate** user acceptance criteria (that's P8-I7)
- ❌ **Does NOT create** production infrastructure - assumes Docker Compose stack is complete

